Row names of a STGrid object.

Source: R/st_grid_class.R
row_names.Rd

The row names of a STGrid object.

row_names(x)

Arguments

x

The STGrid object

Examples

example_dataset()
row_names(Xenium_Mouse_Brain_Coronal_7g)
